author: jpieper
msg: Fix FSFS's handling of empty data representations as pointed out by
jszakmeister.  Two functions were assuming that a data representation
always exists, when in fact it does not always exist.  This fixes a
segfault when reading in node-revisions that lack a "text:" field as
the case when noderev->data_rep is NULL.
